  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cozy simulator of the Water Ring Toss toy from everyone's childhood. Relax while enjoying this frustrating game. Get all the rings on the cone and win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the pressure of water, just like the real thing, and get all of the rings on the cone. Water physics are simulated to make it feel authentic.<br> <br>Local two player co-op also available. Each player gets a toy and both race to win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>List of features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fluid physics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two player local co-op</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cozy atmosphere and calm music</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cozy simulator of the Water Ring Toss toy from everyone's childhood. Relax while enjoying this frustrating game. Get all the rings on the cone and win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control the pressure of water, just like the real thing, and get all of the rings on the cone. Water physics are simulated to make it feel authentic.<br> <br>Local two player co-op also available. Each player gets a toy and both race to win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>List of features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fluid physics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two player local co-op</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cozy atmosphere and calm music</p></li></ul>",
